WHERE: Gordon’s Bay, Western Cape PRICE: R5.95m WHO: Seeff This home has stunning views of False Bay, at a fraction of the cost of a comparable property on Cape Town’s Atlantic seaboard. Set high against the slopes of the Suikerbossie area, it comprises three bedrooms, three reception areas, a large covered patio and a pool. WHERE: Noordhoek, Western Cape PRICE: R39.5m WHO: Pam Golding Properties This beautifully appointed five-bedroom homestead in a prime location in De Goede Hoop, one of Noordhoek’s exclusive equestrian estates, is set among expansive lawns and a dam. Special features include a flatlet with its own entrance, a large swimming pool and a gazebo.